For converting between markdown language and html pandoc is used.

<http://pandoc.org/> a universal document converter.

Instalation instruction: <http://pandoc.org/installing.html>

- Macos: `brew install pandoc`
- Linux: `apt-get install pandoc`

Execution example:

`pandoc -s --section-divs  --css css_file_path.css -o output_file_path.html input_file_path.md`
